@startuml
participant User
box "Cluster" #LightBlue
	participant Frontend
	participant "Cluster mediator"
	participant "Subscriber 1"
	participant "Subscriber N"
	participant "Connection Store"
end box
User -> Frontend: Connect/Disconnect two servers
Frontend -> "Cluster mediator": Connect/disconnect two servers\nTopic: "subscription"
Frontend -> User: ok
"Cluster mediator" --> "Subscriber 1": Connect/disconnect
"Cluster mediator" --> "Subscriber N": Connect/disconnect
note right: Connects/disconnects from the specified node only if\n the message is intended for that subscriber
"Cluster mediator" --> "Connection Store": Connect/disconnect
note right: Stores/removes the connection\n from persistent storage
@enduml